{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-entry-js","path":"/notes/js/array/filter","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"filter"},"html":"<h3>Describing the <code class=\"language-text\">filter</code> Operation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">filter</code> is used for filtering an array based on a condition</li>\n<li>\n<p>It accepts a callback function with the following arguments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">currentValue:</code> Current element processed in the array</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">index</code>: Optional index of <code class=\"language-text\">currentValue</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">array</code>: Optional array that is called</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">thisArg</code>: Optional value to use as <code class=\"language-text\">this</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Defining an Array</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> fruits <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Apple\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Banana\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>fruits<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 2</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Using the <code class=\"language-text\">filter</code> Operation</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Regular function</span>\nfruits<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">item<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> index<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> item<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Array[\"Banana\"]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Arrow function</span>\nfruits<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">item</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> item<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Array[\"Banana\"]</span></code></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"js/array/filter","previousSlug":"js/array/foreach","nextSlug":"js/array/find","previousTitle":"forEach","nextTitle":"find"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}